title: Funnydruids
author: Funnydruids
content: Hi, i got an idea of a company that i want to setup, and i need help to make a website for it. If you got the skills to create a nice website, please add me in telegram https://t.me/PokemonKungenAnd lets talk about it and the price. I already bought the URL and everything, so basicy, just ready to go.Can create it in WorldPress if you want or a sitebuilder on the side. Cheers

comments.author: seoincorporation
comments.body: Hello Funnydruids.I will write you on telegram, I have experience with HTML, CSS, JS, PHP and some content management systems like wordpress. I'm associated with a designer and together we build the Lucky.lat company to offer this kind of services. You can read more about in the project thread. https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=5392842.0 Anyway, i hope we can talk in telegram about your project and make it a reality together.

comments.author: examplens
comments.body: OP, can you give more details about what website you need?what you mentioned is a very broad term, it can be a single HTML page and it can be a complex application that requires a higher level of programming.Also, your budget is a very important thing.

comments.author: Funnydruids
comments.body: The website I want doesn't have to be advanced and only takes 2-3 days to create.So no need for a professional who wants fantasy prices.I've started a little on this one: https://easyinvest.one/(However, this is a finished template, so texts, images and everything must be changed and a lot of information must be entered)I can pay around 200-300 USD if someone can help me, no more. As this is a simple job that goes quickly
